iationen.','Out-of-the-ordinary Alpine hut ambiance near to Zurich, with all kinds of fondue variations. ','Diverses variétés de fondues servies dans une extraordinaire atmosphère de chalet près de Zurich. ','Una straordinaria atmosfera da rifugio vicino a Zurigo, con vari tipi di fondute.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zuerich_chaesalp.jpg','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zuerich_chaesalp_13105.jpg','Einmalige Hüttenatmosphäre','Unique alpine hut atmosphere','Ambiance de vieux chalet','Una straordinaria atmosfera da rifugio',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
