iationen.','Out-of-the-ordinary Alpine hut ambiance near to Zurich, with all kinds of fondue variations. ','Diverses variétés de fondues servies dans une extraordinaire atmosphère de chalet près de Zurich. ','Una straordinaria atmosfera da rifugio vicino a Zurigo, con vari tipi di fondute.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zuerich_chaesalp.jpg','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zuerich_chaesalp_13106.jpg','Schweizer Käsespezialitäten','Swiss cheese specialties','Spécialités suisses','Specialità svizzere','2020-01-26 15:48:00 +0100','Grosse Gruppen','Large groups','Grands groupes','Grandi gruppi','CH','Zürich',8044,'Tobelhofstrasse 236','+41 44 260 75 75','info@chaesalp.ch','http://www.chaesalp.ch',47.382297200000,8.588166600000,'<p>Montag bis Freitag 11.30 &ndash; 14.30 Uhr und 17.30 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr<br>Samstag 10.00 &ndash; 14.30 und 17.30 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr<br>Sonntag 10.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr</p>','<p>Monday&ndash;Friday, 11.30am&ndash;2.30pm &amp; 5.30pm&ndash;12.00 midnight<br>Saturday, 10.00am&ndash;2.30pm &amp; 5.30pm&ndash;12.00 midnigh<br>Sunday, 10.00am&ndash;12.00 midnight</p>','<p>Da lunedì a venerdì dalle 11.30 alle 14.30 e dalle 17.30 alle 24.00<br>Sabato dalle 10.00 alle 14.30 e dalle 17.30 alle 24.00<br>Domenica dalle 10.00 alle 24.00</p>','<p>Da lunedì a venerdì 11.30 – 14.30 e 17.30 – 24.00<br>Sabato 10.00 – 14.30 e 17.30 – 24.00<br>Domenica 10.00 – 24.00</p>','Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday,Sunday','POINT (47.3822972 8.588166599999999)',7,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
