dute e würstel e crauti.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_dezaley_restaurant_1280x960_22691.jpg','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_dezaley_restaurant_1280x960_22689.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 11:59:59 +0200','Schweizer Weine','Swiss wines','Vins suisses','Vini svizzeri','CH','Zürich',8001,'Römergasse 7','+41 44 251 61 29','restaurant@le-dezaley.ch','www.le-dezaley.ch',47.370631500000,8.543778300000,'<p>Montag bis Samstag, 11.30 &ndash; 14.00 Uhr und 18.00 &ndash; 23.00 Uhr</p>','<p>Monday to Saturday, 11.30am &ndash; 2.00pm and 6.00pm &ndash; 11.00pm</p>','<p>Du lundi au samedi, 11h30 &ndash; 14h et 18h &ndash; 23h</p>','<p>Da lunedì a sabato, 11.30 &ndash; 14.00 e 18.00 &ndash; 23.00</p>','Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday','POINT (47.3706315 8.5437783)',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,895750299,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
