es/default/files/keyvisual/web_zuerich_restaurant_oepfelchammer_7447.jpg','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zurich_gastronomie_oepfelchammer_01.jpg','Innenansicht Oepfelchammer','Inside view Oepfelchammer','vue intérieure Oepfelchammer','vista interna Oepfelchammer','2019-09-24 12:03:30 +0200','Altstadt','In the Old Town','Vieille ville','Centro storico','CH','Zürich',8001,'Rindermarkt 12','+41 44 251 23 36',NULL,'http://www.oepfelchammer.ch',47.372333100000,8.544599400000,'<p>Dienstag bis Samstag, 10.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr<br />Samstag 16.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr</p>','<p>Tuesday to Friday, 10.00am &ndash; 12.00am<br />Saturday 4.00pm &ndash; 12.00am</p>','<p>Du mardi au vendredi, 10h &ndash; 24h<br />Samedi 16h &ndash; 24h</p>','<p>Da martedì a venerdì, 10.00 &ndash; 24.00<br />Sabato 16.00 &ndash; 24.00</p>','Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday','POINT (47.3723331 8.544599399999999)',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1498899249,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
